up\\u00a0use\\u00a0this\\u00a0skill\\u00a0to\\u00a0express\\u00a0your\\u00a0ideas\\u00a0to\\u00a0others.<\\/p><p>- <b>Marketing<\\/b>:\\u00a0You\\u00a0would\\u00a0think\\u00a0that\\u00a0I\\u00a0am\\u00a0wrong,\\u00a0but\\u00a0this\\u00a0skill\\u00a0will\\u00a0have\\u00a0it\\u00a0role\\u00a0in\\u00a0the\\u00a0future.\\u00a0Just\\u00a0ask\\u00a0you\\u00a0a\\u00a0question:\\u00a0How\\u00a0can\\u00a0you\\u00a0marketing\\u00a0yourself\\u00a0to\\u00a0others\\u00a0?<\\/p><p>- <b>Speaking<\\/b> :\\u00a0I\\u00a0know\\u00a0that\\u00a0most\\u00a0of\\u00a0developer\\u00a0wont\\u00a0be\\u00a0able\\u00a0to\\u00a0use\\u00a0this\\u00a0skill\\u00a0for\\u00a0most\\u00a0of\\u00a0the\\u00a0working\\u00a0time.\\u00a0This\\u00a0skill\\u00a0in\\u00a0fact\\u00a0just\\u00a0help\\u00a0you\\u00a0communicate\\u00a0with\\u00a0others,\\u00a0and\\u00a0n\\u00a0the\\u00a0future\\u00a0you\\u00a0must\\u00a0upgrade\\u00a0this\\u00a0skill\\u00a0to\\u00a0\\\"<b>Public\\u00a0speaking<\\/b>\\\"\\u00a0skill.\\u00a0If\\u00a0you\\u00a0want\\u00a0to\\u00a0be\\u00a0working\\u00a0as\\u00a0a\\u00a0higher\\u00a0position.<\\/p><hr><p>Thanks\\u00a0for\\u00a0read.\\u00a0Have\\u00a0peace.<\\/p><p>You\\u00a0can\\u00a0follow\\u00a0me\\u00a0on\\u00a0:<\\/p><p>-\\u00a0[<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/step_dev\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">@step_dev<\\/a>](<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/step_dev\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/step_dev<\\/a>) <br><\\/p><p>-\\u00a0[<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/giangvincent.org\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">fb.com\\/giangvincent.org<\\/a>](<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/giangvincent.org\\/\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/giangvincent.org\\/<\\/a>).<\\/p><p>-\\u00a0[<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/giangvincent\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Github.com\\/giangvincent<\\/a>](<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/giangvincent\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">https:\\/\\/github.com\\/giangvincent<\\/a>).<\\/p><p>-\\u00a0[<a href